  <brief_title>PreCoCa - &quot;Prehospital Cooling With Cool-Caps&quot;</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Charite University, Berlin, Germany</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Charite University, Berlin, Germany</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study shall investigate the feasibility of the use of cool-caps in the preclinical
      setting in patients with successful primary cardio-pulmonary resuscitation Hypothesis:
      cool-caps are efficient and feasible to use in the preclinical setting in patients after
      successful CPR.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
